oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Field Diagnosis: Problems and Solutions
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Ashworth, Chris D.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: diagnostic laboratories
method of testing
practical tips
effectiveness
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Results obtained from diagnostic laboratories can be influenced not only by sample quality but also the method of testing itself. In this presentation, I will try to provide practical tips on increasing your effectiveness in using diagnostic services.
